  <title>Optional Tasks</title>

  <para>This appendix contains a reference of all optional tasks, i.e. tasks
  that are not directly needed for building projects, but can assist in
  various aspects of development and deployment.</para>

  <para>This reference lists the tasks alphabetically by the name of the
  classes that implement the tasks. So if you are searching for the reference
  to the <code>&lt;phplint&gt;</code> tag, for example, you will want to look
  at the reference of <classname>PhpLintTask</classname>.</para>
    
